Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.94,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,第六話 被遺忘的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:37.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,入夜也能拍到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:39.50,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,用長時間曝光便能拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:43.29,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,羅拉的木偶行動了\N我去通訊室
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那是親衛隊的機動戰士史摩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:57.83,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你們也有非常好的機動戰士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:00.14,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那還不過是試驗品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:03.01,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那部機動戰士非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:06.41,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,啊    羅拉的機動戰士是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:07.85,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,可惜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:12.86,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:15.89,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,車身寫著蔬果店和書店的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.60,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他們打算偽裝掩人耳目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.91,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他們怎樣把名為「KAPOOL」的\N機動戰士運入市內?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.62,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:34.42,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那個機械木偶在搗亂田地吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:49.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:50.96,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.03,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爺呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.52,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他正前往城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.58,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,一直在這種地方等嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.71,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,應該在格威少爺那裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,用兩部「KAPOOL」去嚇嚇他們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:06.46,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,怎麼會啦\N我們行動的話後方會有6部來幫手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:10.25,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,球型木偶機動力高  會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.17,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭你也要照計劃行事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:13.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.26,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,小姐！不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.37,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.56,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:29.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,快滾！… 不要走來諾克斯市！…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:32.40,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,市民反抗?  是格威教唆的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.01,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下呢!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.64,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這種玩笑是預計之外的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我有信心良民會追隨我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.54,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,但是  任何時代也會有暴民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,在月球也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.01,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這種事情在哪裏都沒區別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.70,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,古今亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:58.26,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:58.97,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是市民軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.32,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,逃回波斯托尼亞城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.20,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你有何企圖!?  格威·萊因福特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:16.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這輛轎車太過注目了\N從這裏能走路回城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.86,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你要我走路!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:19.76,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.79,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,看來很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,女王陛下!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.91,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那麻煩格威先生你帶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我們就是來自那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.51,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,沒那回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你總是那樣子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:40.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,請你令我相信\N迪安娜·索雷爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.78,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那些機械木偶趕到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.78,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,還未有人回報市內的戰況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.69,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,設法牽制它至援軍到來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:53.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,其它部隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,機械木偶正追來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.29,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,好  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:01.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:02.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,如果在這種情況下去你家的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.51,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下會更加危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:10.49,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,波斯托尼亞城堡\N已經準備好送給你們啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.51,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你應該從親衛隊的軍官口中聽過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.39,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不  我們回「向日葵」號去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.51,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,在這裏只會白死！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.33,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,格威·萊因福特先生講得沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.79,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,米蘭執政官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.72,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,握著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:35.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:37.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.60,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,哈利中尉 迪安娜陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:41.50,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,看來還未去到波斯托尼亞城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.80,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那麼陛下在哪裏！?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.54,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那個鬍子來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,請准我攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:50.01,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你別出手 只須牽制士兵便行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那個羅拉的鬍子?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.79,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,親衛隊?在機場的那部史摩?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你別開火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.97,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下說不定就在附近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.90,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,哈利中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.31,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,別過來 如果這傢伙想反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我會想辦法應付
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:26.18,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,打算赤手空拳格鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我給瞧不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.33,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,別過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.72,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,親衛隊史摩的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,比FLAT強得多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,怎辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:44.60,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,停手！羅拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:45.80,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,親衛隊長你也停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:49.43,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,哈利中尉 迪安娜陛下在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:50.97,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,米蘭執政官！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.21,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下平安無事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:57.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,羅拉！不可在諾克斯市內戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:07:00.21,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜回歸軍\N不可被視為好戰份子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.58,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.28,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,真的是迪安娜陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:12.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,有鬍子的機動戰士站不穩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.07,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,想不到地球上也有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,跟史摩同一水平的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.89,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.63,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,有MULTI\NMONITOR嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.19,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,數據處理方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.20,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,沒有敵軍的資料嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.53,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我很羨慕親衛隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.54,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那個叫哈利的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.67,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,也關心迪安娜陛下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.76,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,撤退是什麼回事！?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.76,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我怎知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:17.06,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,上頭有命全軍\N離開諾克斯市20公里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.96,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,即是說作戰失敗了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:25.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是羅蘭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:26.60,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,連那傢伙也撤退！?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.58,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,遵照你的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.85,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍的士兵已經撤離諾克斯市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那是理所當然的措施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:43.49,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,瓦捷上校的事也好\N今日的事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.89,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你們有心談判的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:51.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這件事全因一小撮人獨斷獨行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:56.26,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那麼\N你可以交出那個負責人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我們正在調查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,格威·萊因福特！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.50,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,昨晚的事令我滿身塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:09.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:10.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.42,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你們的房間我亦已經準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.78,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:18.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這邊 請跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:41.18,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,防衛隊去左面！左面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爺也打算談判
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我只好撤退啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你去哪裏? 借來一用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.45,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.39,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我覺得羅蘭有時是個蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你同意嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.72,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我覺得他做起事來很本事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.56,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:00.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他什麼也沒有做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,有武器的話對戰鬥更有幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.76,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,但他卻無心去找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.14,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,援軍來了！停！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.67,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,援軍?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那不是運輸用的火車嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.48,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,從後面把行李搬下來…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,快下車！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,別推我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.28,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,羅拉 蘇絲亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:23.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不是西多老伯嗎 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:27.36,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我想你們協助\N西蓋爾山的發掘工程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.56,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭不在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:33.07,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,KAPOOL不可離開這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:36.26,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,現在停戰中\N機械木偶的數目增加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.86,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,對市民軍也會有利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:38.73,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:42.54,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那就用這列火車\N帶你們兩個回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,竟然要我回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,別發牢騷 我不回去…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,基斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:51.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.71,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,芙蘭怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你不知道她的下落嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.21,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.26,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.67,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,還是熱的 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:22.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是我今早獨個兒烤的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.87,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,獨個兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:27.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,老闆昨晚弄斷肩骨入院了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:31.52,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我去探他\N他把麵包店交託給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:34.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,老闆的太太和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.06,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,還有老闆的住院費
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:39.62,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,以我的能力無法供養他們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:45.60,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下來了啊 會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.80,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,老闆他們會怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:52.68,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,月之民基斯也會烤地球的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.45,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.68,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,設了檢查站嗎！?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.66,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,請停車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.94,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,波斯托尼亞城堡前的公園
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.57,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我拿午餐給朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.54,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你們看 也有好吃的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:30.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這輛電單車是市民軍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我偷回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.42,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我的田地給市民軍搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,給我一個麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.15,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.50,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,芙蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,虧你知道我在這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是基斯告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你想報導月球和地球的會談?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.82,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你認為有人會知道那件事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.82,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,在這兩年以來一直有交涉的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:16.19,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,只好等正式公佈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.69,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,但是\N一定能寫出正面的報導的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:21.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,有多正面?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.46,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,會談一切順利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:27.30,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭你沒有天份寫新聞稿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:31.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是 我什麼天份也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:34.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我做一個域辛鎮的居民便夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下會把問題解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.88,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那便行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:41.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,聽聞她來的目的\N是指揮軍隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那只是傳聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:47.79,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我看各位不懂得\N立體映像是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:49.69,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,於是準備了地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:55.40,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,綠色的部份\N是相信不能住人的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:56.40,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.34,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,北阿米利亞的\NSUNBELT地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.14,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,氣候、風土良好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:02.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,但人口密度卻非常低
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:03.60,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.04,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,猛烈的陽光對身體有害…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:07.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那是北阿米利亞居民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:11.51,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,擁有潛在記憶的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.85,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,記憶告訴你們\N那並非你們的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:15.82,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,所以 我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:18.79,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,歷史根本能隨意被歪曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:23.63,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,誰會容許你們這班人\N現在回歸地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,艾利拿公爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:26.86,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,別阻我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:31.43,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你們提及的黑歷史欠缺證據！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.94,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:37.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你們是拋下地球\N一走了之的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,一走了之！?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:41.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我們的祖先留在這個地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.41,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,令這個星球重生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:46.61,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你們的祖先是卑劣的逃亡者！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,真無禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.26,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,連這種地方也走來偵察?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.49,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不只得一部WODOM啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:05.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞小姐和美雪\N不會胡亂出擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.51,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,雖說市民軍已撤離諾克斯市
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.38,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,但不過退到這種地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那是迪安娜陛下的決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:20.14,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,但是 寶\N迪安娜陛下並非軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,彌補迪安娜陛下不足之處的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,正是我們的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.29,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍正在增強軍力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.99,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那就叫休戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.79,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,去域辛鎮方向偵察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.29,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:39.37,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那班人聚集在那裏做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這裏的人一聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:42.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,便好像會舉行宴會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.70,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,聽聞宇宙人是不進食的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.67,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,吃多些啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:53.62,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,把宇宙人統統趕回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:56.21,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,月之民算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.32,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,WHITE DOLL！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.02,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我們的機械木偶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:12.77,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,叫她們駕駛KAPOOL回去\N太危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:16.17,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,西蓋爾山的發掘工程\N是最優先的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.94,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,他們太不負責任了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.78,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這附近也有WAD的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.41,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,有鬍子的機動戰士行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:27.58,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,怎辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我們的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:32.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是監視集結在這裏的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:36.96,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,多管閒事會給上尉揍一頓的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:43.10,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,敵人接近！是兩腳怪\N敵人接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:46.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不好！\N我不想敵人發現這裏的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:49.64,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜回歸軍的\N「巨型兩腳怪」?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.20,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,美雪 你聽到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:55.65,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你很大聲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:58.01,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,你也很大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:01.71,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不引開敵人的機械木偶不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,知道 待我們出動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:07.86,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,約瑟夫先生 我們要出動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:11.33,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,西多老伯\N這部機能發射飛彈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:15.16,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,未試射過\N你們還是不要發射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,來 快讓她們出動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.36,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,約瑟夫先生雖說這部機很堅固
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:25.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,但不可在近距離被飛彈擊中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:28.91,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不讓他們接近西蓋爾山便行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.63,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,跟在諾克斯市出現的是同類型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.72,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍擁有多少部相同的機體?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.56,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,數目令人擔心\N但機能亦令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.20,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,避過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.81,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,厲害！我們避過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.64,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:06.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,一定應該有武器的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:09.21,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這麼厲害的機動戰士\N沒理由沒武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,顯示出地圖！?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.52,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,好像是域辛鎮的地形…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.92,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是哪個時代的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:19.63,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,毫無準備迎擊敵人\N只會自取滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:23.16,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞小姐\N你不要胡亂出擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.20,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,地底！?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,是WHITE DOLL…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這傢伙去廣場?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:06.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這傢伙…什麼事…！?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.74,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,祭神小屋…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那些岩石…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.82,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,地面…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.47,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,WHITE DOLL的武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,粉碎了！?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那為什麼…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,開玩笑嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,有那麼多武器\N為何只是這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.50,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:14.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞\N不用飛彈收拾不了敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.75,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不那樣做便不能替爸爸報仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:20.24,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,寶 別管那種機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.38,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,它們就像大冬瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,並非大冬瓜的來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那個嗎? 是鬍子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.45,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.93,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,「I-FIELD」輸入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.83,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這樣便行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:40.17,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,沒有帶網來俘虜它！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.97,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,別傷害小姐她們！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.11,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,用手捉住它便行！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:57.95,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那毫無疑問是蠻族的所為！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.32,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,消滅它了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.69,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,地球不是發動戰爭的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.46,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,臭鬍子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.06,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,什麼！?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.64,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,寶！想辦法！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.27,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,狀況不明！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:30.05,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:33.72,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這究竟是什麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:39.55,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那種東西認真戰鬥起來\N很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.86,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.59,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:46.14,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,這個圓球也有用電映出\N圖像的機器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:48.44,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,那叫電視
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:50.94,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我聽西多老伯說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:52.84,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,WHITE DOLL\N的機械木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:54.85,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,會用那種武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:22:00.08,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭 你在駕駛吧\N讓我看見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:08.52,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:12.29,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我求你 這個地球很美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:13.99,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,很優美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:17.09,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不可以在這種地方\N發動戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:21.13,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,做得到的 我什麼也會做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:23.37,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,迪安娜陛下 我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:40.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,第六話 被遺忘的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:42.18,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,不愧是迪安娜陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:45.12,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,為了增進地球\N和月球人之間的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:48.22,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,她提議舉行舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:50.35,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我一定要以\NWHITE DOLL的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:52.83,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,機師羅拉的身份出席
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:55.23,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,因此 我要接受姬艾爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.27,0:23:57.39,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,意想不到的特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:00.97,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,次回 TURN A高達
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.01,0:24:02.94,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,貴婦修行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:06.14,main text,,0000,0000,0050,,我好像風一樣起舞

